headline: Equinix Q4 AFFO & Revenues Miss Estimates but Grow Y/Y, Dividend Hiked
summary: EQIX lags Q4 AFFO and revenue estimates as expenses rise. Recurring revenues increase, and dividend jumps 10%, with upbeat 2026 revenue and AFFO outlook.
